0:From a distance, the island looked much bigger, but that doesn't matter. There are more islands nearby, on which we can build more buildings. All we have to do is connect them with stone bridges.
1:Our ally has the ability to recruit a lecter in the palace. Let's help him provide the right resources to acquire a unit that will take over the mines from the enemy.
2:The island is surrounded by battle ships, so we must also try to obtain naval armament. For this purpose build a shipyard The ally will support us with raw materials, which we may very well need.
